subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description:
1) National Implementation Capacity (NIC)  CD is mainstreamed across practices and at   
    country level
2) Programme and policy advisory services provided at country level
3) Evidence based tools, cases, and guidance material on National Implementation 
    Capacity  -CD is developed
4) Collaborative partnerships developed, strengthened and maintained to multiply impact
subproject.title: DEVELOPMENT OF NATIONAL IMPLEM
